				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "**View**\t\t\nThe generated HTML, CSS, Javascirpt theat is displayed on the UI.\n\nThe view is a passive interface that displays data (the model) and routes \nuser commands (events) to the presenter to act upon that data.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n**Presenter **  \t\nThis is the layer that handles the interaction between the generated UI and the model.\n\nThe presenter acts upon the model and the view. It retrieves data from \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\trepositories (the model), and formats it for display in the view.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n**Model**          \tAn example of a model is subclasses LcsDomainObject.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe model is an interface defining the data to be displayed or otherwise \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tacted upon in the user interface."
			}
		]
